        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I argue that `cython.declare(cython.pointer(cython.double))` == `cython.declare(cython.pointer(float))`\r\nBut I can see that both interpretations can lead to misunderstandings and unexpected behaviour.\r\nNow it's about what will cause less of it",
